---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Premium Home Remodeling Houston"
  description="Terms and conditions for our home remodeling services in Houston, TX."
  activePage="terms"
>
  <header class="page-hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" style="background-image: url('/images/integrales-800.webp')"></div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="hero-tag">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="page-title">Terms of <span class="gold">Service</span></h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Please read these terms carefully before using our services.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-max">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing and using our services, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>2. Services Description</h2>
        <p>We provide professional home remodeling services including kitchen remodeling, bathroom remodeling, whole home renovations, room additions, and exterior remodeling.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>3. Estimates and Pricing</h2>
        <p>All estimates are provided free of charge and are valid for 30 days. Final pricing may vary based on material selections and scope changes approved by the client.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>4. Payment Terms</h2>
        <p>A deposit is required to begin work. Progress payments are due at specified milestones. Final payment is due upon completion and client approval.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>5. Timeline and Completion</h2>
        <p>We strive to complete all projects within the agreed timeline. Delays due to weather, material availability, or change orders may affect the completion date.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>6. Warranty</h2>
        <p>We provide a warranty on workmanship. Specific warranty terms will be outlined in your contract. Manufacturer warranties apply to materials and appliances.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>7. Changes and Modifications</h2>
        <p>Any changes to the scope of work must be requested in writing and may result in additional charges and timeline adjustments.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>8. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@reformat-houston.com<br>
        <strong>Phone:</strong> +1 (832) 555-0100</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }
  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10,10,10,0.95) 0%, rgba(26,26,26,0.85) 100%);
  }
  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #c9a961;
    color: #0a0a0a;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .page-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .gold {
    color: #c9a961;
  }
  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .content-max {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  .content-block {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .content-block h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0a0a0a;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #c9a961;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .content-block p {
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
</style>
